WEBVTT

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:31.520
She did not have children. 
She told us a beautiful story.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:35.120
When she got married and 
tried to have children but could not,

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.760
she started planting trees.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:42.760
And she has created something 
like a forest.

00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:44.960
She still didn’t have a child,

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:49.880
but over forty years,
she had trees all around her.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:54.440
When I wanted to take her picture,
she took me near the forest and sat down.

00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:58.880
She said, “Meet them, 
they are my children.”

00:03:58.910 --> 00:04:01.910
(Applause)